---
title: "onReport (WorkflowRouter)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_extract: workflowId = bytes32(metadata[:32])
    q_extract --> q_check_zero: check workflowId
    q_check_zero --> q_revert_zero: workflowId == bytes32(0)
    q_revert_zero --> [*]: revert InvalidZeroValue()
    q_check_zero --> q_check_allowlist: workflowId != bytes32(0)
    q_check_allowlist --> q_revert_wf: !s_allowlistedWorkflowIds.contains(workflowId)
    q_revert_wf --> [*]: revert WorkflowIdNotAllowlisted(workflowId)
    q_check_allowlist --> q_decode: workflowId is allowlisted
    q_decode --> q_extract_sel: (target, data) = abi.decode(report, (address, bytes))
    q_extract_sel --> q_check_selector: selector = mload(add(data, 32))
    q_check_selector --> q_call: allowlistedSelectors[target].contains(selector)
    q_check_selector --> q_check_target: !allowlistedSelectors[target].contains(selector)
    q_check_target --> q_revert_target: !allowlistedTargets.contains(target)
    q_revert_target --> [*]: revert TargetNotAllowlisted(workflowId, target)
    q_check_target --> q_revert_sel: allowlistedTargets.contains(target)
    q_revert_sel --> [*]: revert SelectorNotAllowlisted(workflowId, target, selector)
    q_call --> [*]: _call(target, data)

    note right of q_extract
        INV-001: caller must have FORWARDER_ROLE (onlyRole modifier)
        INV-002: contract must not be paused (whenNotPaused modifier)
        INV-003: workflowId must be non-zero and allowlisted
        INV-004: target and selector must be allowlisted for the workflowId
        INV-005: selector is extracted from first 4 bytes of data via assembly
    end note
